title: Michael Knowles Tries to Guess Gen-Z Terms | Try to Guess!
description:
Michael Knowles is a master of both no words and words, but how does he stack up when it comes to new words? There are so many new ZOOMER words, from "yeet" to "shook", can Michael guess what these new words mean?
